;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/21\/supplication-fasting-never-turned-away\/","url_meta":{"origin":36058,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: Supplication at breaking fast is never rejected","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the supplication of a fasting person is not turned away at the time of breaking fast .\u201d Abdullah would say when breaking fast, \u201cO Allah, I ask You by You mercy, which encompasses all\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/28\/no-barrier-allah-dawatan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36058,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Nothing to block two supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications have no barrier between them and Allah: the supplication of the oppressed, and the supplication of a man for his brother behind his back.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 11232 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"tex